               <msContents>
                  <summary>I) Taʾāmra Māryām "Miracles of Mary" (fols. 4ra-77vb)&#xD;
I-1) Maṣḥafa śǝrʿāt, Introductory rite of al-Muʿallaqah (fols. 4ra-8ra)&#xD;
I-2) Introductive exhortation and hymns (fols. 8ra-10va)&#xD;
I-3) ʾƎsaggǝd laki wa-ʾǝweddǝsaki ... "I worship Thee ..." (fols. 10va-12rb)&#xD;
I-4) Taʾāmra Māryām "Miracles of Mary": 90 miracles (fols. 12ra-77vb)&#xD;
II) Taʾāmra Giyorgis "Miracles of George": 14 miracles (fols. 78ra-100rb)&#xD;
&#xD;
Additio 1.</summary>
